A CLI tool to create a base template for java classes.

Usage:

```
cargo run "ClassName { $(varName : varType @visibility (modifier1 | modifier2);)* } --optional-flags" target_dir
```

/!\ The double quotes are important /!\

Example: cargo run "Person { name : String @public (final); age : int @private = 0; height : float @protected = 1.5f } --getters --docs" target/

Available flags:

```
--getters: generate getters for all fields
--docs: generate documentation for all fields (Not done yet)
```
